{"id":149675,"date":[{"year":1947,"month":5,"day":7}],"page":"8","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"浮世绘","column":"","genre":"","count":"504","ytitle":"","mtitle":"那时……","ftitle":"(回忆五四以后的那几年)","authors":["冯至"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"冯至"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时觉得既然醒了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就不该"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关着深暗的门窗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时觉得既然醒了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就应该"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放进窗外的光明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处看见新绿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处看见阳光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时像篱　开马棚的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一次望见平原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时像篱　开鸟巢的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一次望见天空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面是旷远。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面是清明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时我们抛下许多的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事物，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管是好还是坏；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时要去追求许多的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事物，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管是近还是远。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的在眼前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的在明天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时我们用简单的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写出简单的诗文；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时我们用幼稚的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写出幼稚的思想。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写的很幼稚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想的也单纯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时父母看见了我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常暗地为我们担忧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时邻人看见了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常在我们背后冷笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们却不管。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们却不顾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时有人无论如何，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要逃出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"室闷的家庭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时有人无论如何，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要舍弃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狭窄的家乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外面在招手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外面在呼唤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时我们是少数，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但相信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个挪威的戏剧家；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时我们是少数，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但相信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个俄国的4革命者。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切为了真理。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切只有互助。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时谁也不会想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在前途"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有无限的艰难；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时谁也不会想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰难时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便会彼此分手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今走了二十多年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却经过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数的岐途与分手；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今走了二十多年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只看见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数的死亡与杀戮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时追求的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在什么地方?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今的平原和天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照映着五月的阳光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今的平原和天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等待看新的眺望。"}]}